A \in F^{MxN}
a_n
A^T
N(A^T) = \{x \in \Re^M : A^Tx = 0\} = \{x \in F^M : \sum\limits_{m=1}^M a_n(m)x(m) = 0 : \forall n = 1,...,N\}
A^T \in F^{NxM}, (A^T)(n,m) := A(m,n)
Ax=0
A^T
A=(a_1\;\ldots\;a_N)
A^T=(a^T_1\;\ldots\;a^T_N)
x=(x(1),\ldots,x(M))^T\in N(A^T)\iff A^Tx=0\iff (a^T_1\;\ldots\;a^T_N)x=0\\\iff (a^T_1x\;\ldots\;a^T_Nx)=0\iff\langle a_n,x\rangle=0,\;\forall n=1,\ldots,N\\\iff\sum_{m=1}^M a_n(m)x(m)=0,\;\forall n=1,\ldots,N 
